{
  "texts": [
    "Liu et al. [78] reviewed the historical development of radar and communications from a signal processing perspective.In addition, some surveys delved into the specific applications of ISAC.",
    "For example, Cui et al. [11] delved into the different applications of ISAC in IoT.",
    "Zhong et al. [22] gave an overview of ISAC-enabled V2X and discussed the key technologies involved, such as predictive beamforming.",
    "Zhang et al. [79] provided a comprehensive overview of ISAC enablement in mobile networks, focusing on the signal processing techniques.",
    "Meng et al. [80] reviewed the UAV-enabled ISAC and proposed several schemes for performance enhancement."
  ]
}